==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[steam]] [[engine]]}}

# Any [[heat]] [[engine]] that uses steam as its primary working fluid to do [[mechanical]] [[work]].
# {{UK}} A steam-powered [[locomotive]].
# a [[motor]] that performs mechanical work when supplied by steam from a separate source.
# (common usage) specifically a piston engine driven by steam as opposed to a different steam driven engine such as a steam turbine.

